## User Presence Sidebar Feature

### Requirements:
- [ ] Add sidebar on the left side of room (same side as "Save Chat" button)
- [ ] Display UI with everyone who has entered this specific room
- [ ] Show "Online" status with green color for users currently in room
- [ ] Show "Off" status with red color for users who left
- [ ] Sidebar must NOT overlap the chat part of the screen
- [ ] DO NOT CHANGE THE SIZES OF ANYTHING except the sidebar
- [ ] Keep users who left in the sidebar with offline status
- [ ] If user comeback to the room, change back to Online
- [ ] Remove users from sidebar after 45 minutes if they don't return
- [ ] Add hide/show toggle functionality